    <body><p><span rend="main_text" rendition="div"><lb />
<span rend="jisage_5" rendition="div" style="margin-left: 5em"><span rend="sho1" style="font-size: small;">――汽車の窓にて</span></span>
<lb />
夏の日の<span type="ruby"><span type="rb">午</span><span type="rp">（</span><span type="rt">ひる</span><span type="rp">）</span></span>さがり、<lb />
<span type="ruby"><span type="rb">我</span><span type="rp">（</span><span type="rt">わ</span><span type="rp">）</span></span>が<span type="ruby"><span type="rb">汽車</span><span type="rp">（</span><span type="rt">きしや</span><span type="rp">）</span></span>は<span type="ruby"><span type="rb">物憂</span><span type="rp">（</span><span type="rt">ものう</span><span type="rp">）</span></span>げに<lb />
黒き煙を<span type="ruby"><span type="rb">息吹</span><span type="rp">（</span><span type="rt">いぶ</span><span type="rp">）</span></span>きつゝ、<lb />
<span type="ruby"><span type="rb">炎天</span><span type="rp">（</span><span type="rt">えんてん</span><span type="rp">）</span></span>の<span type="ruby"><span type="rb">東海道</span><span type="rp">（</span><span type="rt">とうかいどう</span><span type="rp">）</span></span>を西へ馳す。<lb />
<span type="ruby"><span type="rb">世</span><span type="rp">（</span><span type="rt">よ</span><span type="rp">）</span></span>ゆゑ、はたわれからの<lb />
<span type="ruby"><span type="rb">黒熱</span><span type="rp">（</span><span type="rt">こくねつ</span><span type="rp">）</span></span>に<span type="ruby"><span type="rb">膿</span><span type="rp">（</span><span type="rt">う</span><span type="rp">）</span></span>み<span type="ruby"><span type="rb">爛</span><span type="rp">（</span><span type="rt">ただ</span><span type="rp">）</span></span>れ、<lb />
<span type="ruby"><span type="rb">灰汗</span><span type="rp">（</span><span type="rt">あく</span><span type="rp">）</span></span>の<span rend="notes">［＃「灰汗の」はママ］</span><span type="ruby"><span type="rb">洪水</span><span type="rp">（</span><span type="rt">でみず</span><span type="rp">）</span></span>の<span type="ruby"><span type="rb">胸底</span><span type="rp">（</span><span type="rt">むなぞこ</span><span type="rp">）</span></span>の<lb />
<span type="ruby"><span type="rb">政</span><span type="rp">（</span><span type="rt">まつり</span><span type="rp">）</span></span>の<span type="ruby"><span type="rb">庁</span><span type="rp">（</span><span type="rt">ちやう</span><span type="rp">）</span></span>を<span type="ruby"><span type="rb">失</span><span type="rp">（</span><span type="rt">うしな</span><span type="rp">）</span></span>ひし<lb />
<span type="ruby"><span type="rb">病人</span><span type="rp">（</span><span type="rt">やまうど</span><span type="rp">）</span></span>なれば、<span type="ruby"><span type="rb">天地</span><span type="rp">（</span><span type="rt">あめつち</span><span type="rp">）</span></span>の<lb />
<span type="ruby"><span type="rb">眺望</span><span type="rp">（</span><span type="rt">ながめ</span><span type="rp">）</span></span>ことごと<span type="ruby"><span type="rb">灰</span><span type="rp">（</span><span type="rt">はひ</span><span type="rp">）</span></span><span type="ruby"><span type="rb">濁</span><span type="rp">（</span><span type="rt">た</span><span type="rp">）</span></span>みて、<lb />
あゝうたてしや、ひたぶるに、<span type="ruby"><span type="rb">涙</span><span type="rp">（</span><span type="rt">なみだ</span><span type="rp">）</span></span>ぞ落つる。<lb />
乗合は<span type="ruby"><span type="rb">背</span><span type="rp">（</span><span type="rt">せな</span><span type="rp">）</span></span>と<span type="ruby"><span type="rb">背</span><span type="rp">（</span><span type="rt">せな</span><span type="rp">）</span></span><lb />
<span type="ruby"><span type="rb">肩</span><span type="rp">（</span><span type="rt">かた</span><span type="rp">）</span></span><span type="ruby"><span type="rb">犇々</span><span type="rp">（</span><span type="rt">ひし／＼</span><span type="rp">）</span></span>とすりあひぬ。<lb />
近江を過ぎて京ちかき<lb />
<span type="ruby"><span type="rb">山科</span><span type="rp">（</span><span type="rt">やましな</span><span type="rp">）</span></span>や、<span type="ruby"><span type="rb">竹</span><span type="rp">（</span><span type="rt">たけ</span><span type="rp">）</span></span>の<span type="ruby"><span type="rb">入日</span><span type="rp">（</span><span type="rt">いりひ</span><span type="rp">）</span></span>に、<lb />
<span type="ruby"><span type="rb">鬱憂</span><span type="rp">（</span><span type="rt">うつゆう</span><span type="rp">）</span></span>のこゝろは<span type="ruby"><span type="rb">重</span><span type="rp">（</span><span type="rt">おも</span><span type="rp">）</span></span>く、<lb />
<span type="ruby"><span type="rb">倦</span><span type="rp">（</span><span type="rt">う</span><span type="rp">）</span></span>じ疲れたる目はひと目<lb />
<span type="ruby"><span type="rb">線路</span><span type="rp">（</span><span type="rt">せんろ</span><span type="rp">）</span></span>の<span type="ruby"><span type="rb">砂</span><span type="rp">（</span><span type="rt">すな</span><span type="rp">）</span></span>に――あゝこの時、<lb />
胸はまた<span type="ruby"><span type="rb">膿</span><span type="rp">（</span><span type="rt">う</span><span type="rp">）</span></span>みて<span type="ruby"><span type="rb">潰</span><span type="rp">（</span><span type="rt">つぶ</span><span type="rp">）</span></span>れぬ。<lb />
<span type="ruby"><span type="rb">見</span><span type="rp">（</span><span type="rt">み</span><span type="rp">）</span></span>よ、<span type="ruby"><span type="rb">鉄道</span><span type="rp">（</span><span type="rt">てつだう</span><span type="rp">）</span></span>の<span type="ruby"><span type="rb">枕木</span><span type="rp">（</span><span type="rt">まくらぎ</span><span type="rp">）</span></span>は、<lb />
<span type="ruby"><span type="rb">癒</span><span type="rp">（</span><span type="rt">い</span><span type="rp">）</span></span>ゆべからざる<span type="ruby"><span type="rb">病人</span><span type="rp">（</span><span type="rt">やまうど</span><span type="rp">）</span></span>の<lb />
<span type="ruby"><span type="rb">素枯</span><span type="rp">（</span><span type="rt">すが</span><span type="rp">）</span></span>れはてたる<span type="ruby"><span type="rb">肋骨</span><span type="rp">（</span><span type="rt">あばら</span><span type="rp">）</span></span>なり。<lb />
と見る、また<span type="ruby"><span type="rb">我</span><span type="rp">（</span><span type="rt">わ</span><span type="rp">）</span></span>が乗る<span type="ruby"><span type="rb">汽車</span><span type="rp">（</span><span type="rt">きしや</span><span type="rp">）</span></span>は<lb />
痩せて<span type="ruby"><span type="rb">細</span><span type="rp">（</span><span type="rt">ほそ</span><span type="rp">）</span></span>れる<span type="ruby"><span type="rb">肋骨</span><span type="rp">（</span><span type="rt">ろくこつ</span><span type="rp">）</span></span>を<lb />
<span type="ruby"><span type="rb">毒</span><span type="rp">（</span><span type="rt">どく</span><span type="rp">）</span></span>ある<span type="ruby"><span type="rb">牙</span><span type="rp">（</span><span type="rt">きば</span><span type="rp">）</span></span>に<span type="ruby"><span type="rb">噛</span><span type="rp">（</span><span type="rt">か</span><span type="rp">）</span></span>みてゆく<lb />
<span type="ruby"><span type="rb">黒蛇</span><span type="rp">（</span><span type="rt">くろへび</span><span type="rp">）</span></span>よ、あゝ<span type="ruby"><span type="rb">死</span><span type="rp">（</span><span type="rt">し</span><span type="rp">）</span></span>の<span type="ruby"><span type="rb">使</span><span type="rp">（</span><span type="rt">つか</span><span type="rp">）</span></span>ひ。――<lb />
『無明』の子なる<span type="ruby"><span type="rb">病人</span><span type="rp">（</span><span type="rt">やまうど</span><span type="rp">）</span></span>は、<lb />
をさな心にいとせめて<lb />
<span type="ruby"><span type="rb">垂乳根</span><span type="rp">（</span><span type="rt">たらちね</span><span type="rp">）</span></span>の膝まくら<lb />
しばし<span type="ruby"><span type="rb">安睡</span><span type="rp">（</span><span type="rt">やすい</span><span type="rp">）</span></span>の夢見むと、<lb />
<span type="ruby"><span type="rb">指</span><span type="rp">（</span><span type="rt">さ</span><span type="rp">）</span></span>す<span type="ruby"><span type="rb">故郷</span><span type="rp">（</span><span type="rt">ふるさと</span><span type="rp">）</span></span>の<span type="ruby"><span type="rb">琉球</span><span type="rp">（</span><span type="rt">りうきう</span><span type="rp">）</span></span>は<lb />
五百里さかる海の島、<lb />
われを載せたる<span type="ruby"><span type="rb">黒蛇</span><span type="rp">（</span><span type="rt">くろへび</span><span type="rp">）</span></span>は<lb />
<span type="ruby"><span type="rb">勢</span><span type="rp">（</span><span type="rt">いきほ</span><span type="rp">）</span></span>ひ<span type="ruby"><span type="rb">猛</span><span type="rp">（</span><span type="rt">まう</span><span type="rp">）</span></span>に、こは如何に、<lb />
その<span type="ruby"><span type="rb">故郷</span><span type="rp">（</span><span type="rt">ふるさと</span><span type="rp">）</span></span>も<span type="ruby"><span type="rb">行過</span><span type="rp">（</span><span type="rt">ゆきす</span><span type="rp">）</span></span>ぎつ、<lb />
右に横たふ<span type="ruby"><span type="rb">山脈</span><span type="rp">（</span><span type="rt">やまなみ</span><span type="rp">）</span></span>は<lb />
はや<span type="ruby"><span type="rb">冥府</span><span type="rp">（</span><span type="rt">よみ</span><span type="rp">）</span></span>の<span type="ruby"><span type="rb">国</span><span type="rp">（</span><span type="rt">くに</span><span type="rp">）</span></span>、血に染めし<lb />
<span type="ruby"><span type="rb">硫黄</span><span type="rp">（</span><span type="rt">いわう</span><span type="rp">）</span></span>の池も近づくよ、<lb />
あなゆるせやと<span type="ruby"><span type="rb">唸</span><span type="rp">（</span><span type="rt">うめ</span><span type="rp">）</span></span>き伏し、<lb />
やゝありて<span type="ruby"><span type="rb">我</span><span type="rp">（</span><span type="rt">われ</span><span type="rp">）</span></span>にかへれば、<lb />
<span type="ruby"><span type="rb">京</span><span type="rp">（</span><span type="rt">きやう</span><span type="rp">）</span></span>は<span type="ruby"><span type="rb">水無月</span><span type="rp">（</span><span type="rt">みなづき</span><span type="rp">）</span></span>、<span type="ruby"><span type="rb">祇園会</span><span type="rp">（</span><span type="rt">ぎをんゑ</span><span type="rp">）</span></span>の<lb />
<span type="ruby"><span type="rb">空</span><span type="rp">（</span><span type="rt">そら</span><span type="rp">）</span></span>うつくしき<span type="ruby"><span type="rb">星月夜</span><span type="rp">（</span><span type="rt">ほしづきよ</span><span type="rp">）</span></span>、<lb />
我が汽車はしづしづと<lb />
涙さしぐむ<span type="ruby"><span type="rb">哀音</span><span type="rp">（</span><span type="rt">あいおん</span><span type="rp">）</span></span>の<lb />
汽笛して<span type="ruby"><span type="rb">七条</span><span type="rp">（</span><span type="rt">しちぜう</span><span type="rp">）</span></span>出でぬ。<lb />
<lb />
<lb />
<lb />
</span></p></body>
